    <summary>
      <para>Type: <b><a href="https://docs.microsoft.com//windows/desktop/WinProg/windows-data-types">BYTE</a></b></para>
      <para>Boolean value indicating whether to save the vertex shader state.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
